readable.content: A dog leaps over a man in a white cap to catch and orange Frisbee . A dog leaps over a man to catch a disc . A man wearing sunglasses kneels with one knee on the ground looks up to see a dog in the air catching an orange Frisbee . Dog jumps over owner to catch smilely faced Frisbee , while spectators in the park watch Several people are standing and sitting on a grassy field watching a dog jump over a man to catch an orange Frisbee .
